# ğŸŒ± Kindora

**Kindora** is an open-source full-stack platform built to empower people and non-profit organizations by enabling the donation, exchange, and management of goods, events, and volunteer opportunities. Kindora offers secure authentication, real-time communication, role-based access, and a dedicated space for NGOs to thrive.

